---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`about | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="About WiredIn Infosec Team"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>about wiredin</h1>
			<p>
				Team <b>WiredIn</b> is the official InfoSec team under the{" "}
				<a href="https://pclub.in" target="_blank">Programming Club, IIT Kanpur</a>. The team has a
				diverse group of security enthusiasts passionate about tackling
				challenges across Cryptography, Binary Exploitation, Reverse
				Engineering, Forensics, and Web Security.
			</p>
			<p>
				Through our regular meetups, training sessions, and internal
				CTFs, the knmowledge and skills, which the team members gained, are passed onto junior batches. We
				consistently rank high globally in competitive Capture The Flag
				competitions.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
		<style>
			main {
				max-width: 720px;
				min-height: 50vh;
			}
			h1 {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			p {
				color: var(--fg-muted);
				line-height: 1.8;
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
